# These tests fail on Linux because kPromptForDownload defaults to true,
# triggering the GTK file chooser dialog which causes g_malloc leaks
# detected by LSan on ASAN builds and timeouts.
# https://github.com/brave/brave-browser/issues/52572
# https://github.com/brave/brave-browser/issues/52649
# https://github.com/brave/brave-browser/issues/52569
-All/PDFPluginDisabledTest.DirectNavigationToPDF/*
-ChromeMojoProxyResolverFactoryBrowserTest.*
-PluginResponseInterceptorURLLoaderThrottleBrowserTest.DownloadPdf
